name: AJ and the Queen
overview: While traveling across the country in a run-down RV, drag queen Ruby Red discovers an unlikely sidekick in AJ: a tough-talking 10-year-old stowaway.

episodes.name: New York City
episodes.overview: The story begins at the end of an era as Robert (aka Ruby Red) prepares for a new adventure. Elsewhere, young AJ endures the mean streets of Manhattan.

episodes.name: Pittsburgh
episodes.overview: Robert treats AJ to breakfast ... and a long list of questions. Later, Ruby steps back into the spotlight and encounters bad blood, on and offstage.

episodes.name: Columbus
episodes.overview: A fender bender leads to a frantic game of cat and mouse. AJ receives a message from back home, and Ruby prepares for an impromptu competition.

episodes.name: Louisville
episodes.overview: AJ and Robert encounter a new cast of queens as Ruby gets ready for a daring performance. Meanwhile, Damien’s cruel game claims another victim.

episodes.name: Mt. Juliet
episodes.overview: As the tour heads to Nashville, a peculiar pit stop catches Robert's eye, and AJ makes a crafty plan for extra cash.

episodes.name: Little Rock
episodes.overview: A late-night rest stop leads to a last-minute musical as Robert makes friends in a rural RV park. Meanwhile, his history with "Hector" comes to light.

episodes.name: Jackson
episodes.overview: Robert and AJ make their way to Mississippi for an action-packed reunion. Back in New York, Louis opens the door to an unexpected visitor.

episodes.name: Baton Rouge
episodes.overview: A medical emergency triggers a string of painful memories for AJ and Robert. Lady Danger and Damien cross paths with a fellow traveler.

episodes.name: Fort Worth
episodes.overview: As the RV rolls into Texas, the tour hits an unforeseen snag. Robert reconnects with an old friend, and AJ eagerly awaits life with Pop Pop.

episodes.overview: The end of tour arrives as Ruby competes in Miss Drag USA, AJ prepares for Pop Pop's farm, and Brianna attempts one last desperate leap of faith.
